(text "NOTES:" (at 20.32 205.74 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 9235100e-8a5c-5b13-9db0-dd6f829c04ab))
(text "Dorji pinout: pins 9/10 GND; pins 2/4/11/13/14/15 NC; pin12 ANT 50 ohm; pin16 RXD; pin17 TXD." (at 20.32 213.36 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid b9ab3a3a-cb2e-5ead-a967-07b8393a5a82))
(text "H/L is never driven high: fitted 0R selects low power; omitted 0R floats for high power only after RF release." (at 20.32 220.98 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid aced40fb-f391-51da-a563-4961dace7a89))
(text "FL240 LFCN-160+ (8W at 25C) and FL250 ULP-470+ (2W) are fitted LPFs; calculate both 50-ohm launches from the final stackup." (at 20.32 228.6 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 422813fb-bb21-5141-8b06-298ccef4b711))
(text "PE42820 is rated 43dBm CW through 2GHz when powered; RADIO_4V0 powers switch and module together." (at 20.32 236.22 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid d5f7c835-c759-5d42-a7aa-a9cf0e1e6dcd))
(text "A true 2m PCB antenna is laptop-scale-impractical; use a loaded internal/enclosure antenna feed or rear external whip." (at 20.32 243.84 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 8d4f8e5f-d6dc-5e08-895f-9ec5824a5d76))
(text "Validate antenna match/VSWR, enclosure detuning, duty cycle, harmonics, and GNSS/Wi-Fi isolation before RF release." (at 20.32 251.46 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid ac483df7-2c2b-5d7c-8580-7c361a886a51))
(text "GPS APRS support is software/audio-path work using the MAX-M10S sheet and the VHF radio path." (at 20.32 259.08 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid ae9ab2a0-6ece-5e73-8cf7-b24ee3bf932e))
(text "U260/U261 force both radios out of TX for simultaneous requests; U241/U251 freeze antenna selection for the full transmit interval." (at 20.32 266.7 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 36439ef9-229c-5435-bb3f-bf674f7f003f))
(text "R229/R231 select 0.5W prototype power. Filter ratings do not prove emissions compliance; verify both outputs on a spectrum analyzer." (at 20.32 274.32 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 363b5223-5c81-5baf-963f-8d8bac95bd75))
(text "R225/R226 and R235-R238 keep both modules asleep and PTT inactive through connector faults, reset, and rail ramp." (at 20.32 281.94 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 99b184d7-5ef3-5965-b077-48c93df7d231))
(text "Firmware wake sequence: assert PD high, wait at least 500ms, complete/retry DMOCONNECT plus configuration, then allow PTT." (at 20.32 289.56 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid dfdbd127-4c2e-5f1e-aa18-bb3b120c54e2))
(text "C270-C275 guarantee 0VDC at all PE42820 RF ports; verify their 50-ohm launches and both antenna paths with a VNA." (at 20.32 297.18 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 33bd2903-59ea-5032-bae7-bc887d6921e0))
